Build installation
------------------

The build process uses cmake. Basic usage on UNIX

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
su
make install

Dependencies
------------

Required:

- CUDA toolkit >= 2.1 (SDK not required)
- Boost

Optional:

- Doxygen (for man-page generation)

Usage
-----

The 'examples' directory contains an example network using the C++ API.

On UNIX, the build process generates man pages (if Doxgyen is installed). Check
'man 3 nemo.h' for C API reference and 'man 3 nemo::Network' for a C++ API
reference.

Andreas Fidjeland
